<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/images/favicon.png">
    <meta name="description"
        content="Organize your entryway for better home flow. Discover smart shoe storage, hook systems, and decor ideas that keep your foyer tidy and welcoming.">
